sentences.english: The remaining places on the Middletons' front row are yet to be confirmed.
sentences.chinese: 剩余的座位安排尚有待确定。

sentences.english: And we scheduled it and we get it and my dad and my sister would help trim it.
sentences.chinese: 先做安排然后实践，爸爸和姐姐会帮忙修剪圣诞树。

sentences.english: As you can see, there are some consequences with the current arrangement.
sentences.chinese: 正如您所看到的，当前这种安排还存有许多问题。

sentences.english: As for whether he will visit the DPRK, I am not aware of such an arrangement.
sentences.chinese: 至于他是否去朝鲜，目前我没有听说有这方面的安排。

sentences.english: In the beginning the training sessions were held at Volvo Trucks dealerships on Saturdays.
sentences.chinese: 最初的培训课程由沃尔沃卡车公司安排在周日进行。

sentences.english: The workers phased the various processes in shirt production.
sentences.chinese: 工人们安排好衬衣生产的各道工序。

sentences.english: L2. Due to the destination is an inland city, we have to arrange sea-land intermodal transportation.
sentences.chinese: 由于目的地是内陆城市，我们只好安排海陆联运。

sentences.english: No matter how carefully I plan my time, the plan always goes wrong.
sentences.chinese: 不论怎么仔细安排时间，我的计划总是出问题。

sentences.english: I dovetailed my work arrangements with hers.
sentences.chinese: 我把自己的工作和她的工作做了妥善安排。

sentences.english: We can reset the seam and take in some of the material.
sentences.chinese: 我们可以重新安排缝口，并收进一点衣料。

sentences.english: Add a loop or make a schedule to generate large data volumes.
sentences.chinese: 添加一个循环或者做一个安排以生成大型的数据集。

sentences.english: Three, we will spend the excess revenue in the central government budget in an appropriate way.
sentences.chinese: 三是合理安排中央财政超收收入。

sentences.english: The letter added that counselling had been arranged for pupils and staff.
sentences.chinese: 信中说，已为学生和教职员工安排了心理咨询。

sentences.english: And the test arrangement is the important constituent part of the educational administration management.
sentences.chinese: 而考场安排管理系统是教务管理系统的重要组成部分。

sentences.english: No, I don't think I have any plans. Why do you ask?
sentences.chinese: 不忙，我想我没什么安排。你问来干嘛？

sentences.english: You have other plans on a Wednesday afternoon?
sentences.chinese: 难道你星期三下午还有其他安排吗？
